data.description: Experience luxury living in this stunning Lakeview Home with a Pool in Melrose Landing. Built in 2001 on a 5,500 sq ft lot, this 5-bed, 4-bath gem boasts 3,745 total sq ft. Abundant natural light fills the formal living and dining rooms, complemented by a 1 Bed/1 Bath Downstairs next to the laundry room and converted garage for additional space for multi-generational families. Step outside to a covered terrace and indulge in the tranquil pool. Nestled in a quiet, family-oriented neighborhood, this haven is minutes away from excellent schools, shopping centers, and restaurants. Embrace comfort and style in this perfect family retreat.
